name: Marincess Blue Slug
desc:
1 Level 4 or lower "Marincess" monster
You can only Link Summon "Marincess Blue Slug(s)" once per turn. If this card is Link Summoned: You can target 1 "Marincess" monster in your GY, except "Marincess Blue Slug"; add it to your hand, also you cannot Special Summon monsters for the rest of this turn, except WATER monsters.
